rollDiceAction

protected void rollDiceAction()
Roles both dice at the same time Calculates two dice roles and changes the dice faces on the board. Then moves the ball the distance of the value of the largest dice (plus one for doubles).

Has the view move the ball a specific number of lines If currentPlayer is player #1 then move the ball towards the away goal, and if player #2 then move the ball towards the home goal. If the currentLine is 11 or -11 then change the game state to SHOT_STATE.
